RelatedSentence: SELBYVILLE - State troopers are conducting a death investigation after a male and female were found dead in the parking lot in the rear of the Bayview Estates community clubhouse .

According to Delaware State Police spokesman Cpl. John Day , troopers responded to the clubhouse on Sea Gull Road shortly before 6 a.m. this morning after receiving a report of two people lying on the ground in the rear parking lot .
